reviewText: Video was interview only, but good seller!
no actual footage of his career moments. all discussion.
The one good thing, is that it really has Ted Williams in it.  But I really wanted to see some videos of his hitting with him explaining it.  A little too boring for me.
This is a good show! Ted Williams is quite a character!
Brings back memories of the old time red sox  and what a great hitter he was.
It was a pleasure to listen to the greatest hitter of the last 75 years speak. Insightful and informative words concerning perceptions of the press and batting over .400.
